description=Camera bringup facilitation: (1) HOOKS — boot-persistent frida injection of the opt-in probe set (service.sh); (2) PATCHES — systemless context-preserving bind-mount overlay of validated vendor/odm blobs (post-fs-data.sh, replace-existing-only, disable-gated). Both INERT until configured. No whole-partition overlay, no camxoverridesettings.txt — avoids the 2026-06-13 bootloop class. Fails safe; never blocks boot. doc-50.
